question: Which among the following famous personality was not born in Madhya Pradesh?
explanation:
Chandra Shekhar Azad-born on 23 July 1906 in Bhavra village, in the present-day Alirajpur district of Madhya Pradesh
Bhimrao Ramji Ambedkar- born on 14 April 1891 in the town and military cantonment of Mhow in the Central Provinces (now in Madhya Pradesh)
Vishwanath Pratap Singh-25 June 1931 Allahabad, United Provinces.
Atal Bihari Vajpayee-December 25, 1924 in Gwalior.
